    <title>Hexo &amp; Theme Usage</title>
    <url>/2020/06/07/hello-world/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<html><head></head><body><p><a href="https://hexo.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hexo</a>, <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">documentation</a>, <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">troubleshooting</a>, <a href="https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub Issues</a>.</p>
<h1 id="Hexo"><a href="#Hexo" class="headerlink" title="Hexo"></a>Hexo</h1><h2 id="Install-amp-Setup"><a href="#Install-amp-Setup" class="headerlink" title="Install &amp; Setup"></a>Install &amp; Setup</h2><p></p><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p>
<h2 id="Initialize"><a href="#Initialize" class="headerlink" title="Initialize"></a>Initialize</h2><p></p><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">$ <span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> &lt;folder&gt;</span><br><span class="line">$ npm install</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p>
<p>File Structure:</p>
<p></p><figure class="highlight python hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">|-- _config.yml <span class="hljs-comment"># configuration file for hexo</span></span><br><span class="line">|-- source</span><br><span class="line">    |-- _posts</span><br><span class="line">        |-- one_blog.md <span class="hljs-comment"># blog file</span></span><br><span class="line">    |-- _drafts</span><br><span class="line">        |-- one_draft.md <span class="hljs-comment"># draft file</span></span><br><span class="line">|-- themes</span><br><span class="line">    |-- landscape <span class="hljs-comment"># default theme</span></span><br><span class="line">    |-- ocean </span><br><span class="line">        |-- _config.yml <span class="hljs-comment"># configuration file for ocean</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p>
<h2 id="Create-a-new-post"><a href="#Create-a-new-post" class="headerlink" title="Create a new post"></a>Create a new post</h2><p></p><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new <span class="hljs-string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span> / $ hexo n <span class="hljs-string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p>
<p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Writing</a></p>
<h2 id="Run-server"><a href="#Run-server" class="headerlink" title="Run server"></a>Run server</h2><p></p><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo server / $ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p>
<p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Server</a></p>
<h2 id="Generate-static-files"><a href="#Generate-static-files" class="headerlink" title="Generate static files"></a>Generate static files</h2><p></p><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo generate / $ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p>
<p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Generating</a></p>
<h2 id="Deploy-to-remote-sites"><a href="#Deploy-to-remote-sites" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to remote sites"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h2><p></p><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo deploy / $ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p>
<p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Deployment</a></p>
<h2 id="Deploy-to-github"><a href="#Deploy-to-github" class="headerlink" title="Deploy to github"></a>Deploy to github</h2><p></p><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ yarn add hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p>
<p>Then, go to hexo&#x2019;s _config.yml, add this to deploy session:</p>
<p></p><figure class="highlight yml hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="hljs-attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="hljs-attr">repo:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://github.com/xyshell/xyshell.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="hljs-attr">branch:</span> <span class="hljs-string">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p>
<h1 id="Theme"><a href="#Theme" class="headerlink" title="Theme"></a>Theme</h1><h2 id="Install-amp-Setup-amp-Update"><a href="#Install-amp-Setup-amp-Update" class="headerlink" title="Install &amp; Setup &amp; Update"></a>Install &amp; Setup &amp; Update</h2><p></p><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ git <span class="hljs-built_in">clone</span> https://github.com/zhwangart/hexo-theme-ocean.git themes/ocean</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p>
<p>Modify theme setting in hexo&#x2019;s _config.yml to ocean:</p>
<p></p><figure class="highlight yml hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="hljs-attr">theme:</span> <span class="hljs-string">ocean</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p>
<p>Further update:</p>
<p></p><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> themes/ocean</span><br><span class="line">git pull</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p>
<h1 id="Theme-Reference"><a href="#Theme-Reference" class="headerlink" title="Theme Reference"></a>Theme Reference</h1><h2 id="Ocean"><a href="#Ocean" class="headerlink" title="Ocean"></a>Ocean</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/zhwangart/hexo-theme-ocean" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/zhwangart/hexo-theme-ocean</a></p>
<h2 id="Minos"><a href="#Minos" class="headerlink" title="Minos"></a>Minos</h2><p><a href="https://github.com/ppoffice/hexo-theme-minos" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://github.com/ppoffice/hexo-theme-minos</a></p>
</body></html>]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>Hexo</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
