    <content><![CDATA[<html><head></head><body><h1 id="SSH"><a href="#SSH" class="headerlink" title="SSH"></a>SSH</h1><pre><code class="bash">ssh -i &lt;path-to-pem&gt; admin@&lt;ip/dns&gt;</code></pre>
<h1 id="SCP"><a href="#SCP" class="headerlink" title="SCP"></a>SCP</h1><pre><code class="bash">scp -i &lt;path-to-pem&gt; &lt;path-to-source-file&gt; admin@&lt;ip/dns&gt;:/home/admin/&lt;path-to-target-file&gt;</code></pre>
</body></html>]]></content>
