    <title>AWS Note</title>
    <url>/2020/06/08/aws-note/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<html><head></head><body><h1 id="AWS-CLI"><a href="#AWS-CLI" class="headerlink" title="AWS CLI"></a>AWS CLI</h1><h2 id="Upload-folder-to-S3"><a href="#Upload-folder-to-S3" class="headerlink" title="Upload folder to S3"></a>Upload folder to S3</h2><p></p><figure class="highlight bash hljs"><table><tbody><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">aws s3 cp &lt;path-to-source-folder&gt; s3://&lt;path-to-target-folder&gt; --recursive --exclude <span class="hljs-string">&quot;.DS_Store&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p>
</body></html>]]></content>
